<node id="&quot;SIDNEY ZION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Sidney E. Zion was an American writer born on November 14, 1933, in Passaic, NJ, and passed away on August 2, 2009, in Brooklyn. He authored several works including 'Markers', 'Begin from Beginning', 'Read All About It', 'Trust Your Mother But Cut the Cards', 'Loyalty and Betrayal: The Story of the American Mob', and 'Markers' (a novel). He also co-authored 'The Autobiography of Roy Cohn' and was a co-founder and co-editor of 'Scanlan's Monthly' magazine."</data>
